msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=utf-8\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Today’s topic is about what teens see online. Teens may come across confusing, upsetting, or unrealistic content. As parents, we can feel unsure how to talk about this. By staying calm and talking together, you can help your teen feel safe and make good choices online."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Many teens come across sexual content online, often without looking for it. They may feel curious, confused or uncomfortable. These feelings are normal. Talking together helps your teen understand that not everything they see online is real, and learn what respectful, healthy relationships look like."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_1.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hear how @data.characters.media_female_1.name learned to talk to her teen about what they see online"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The other day, my son told me that a sexual video had popped up on his phone. I didn’t know what to say and I wanted to panic, but instead I listened first and we could talk. It was an uncomfortable conversation, but I'm glad we had it. Now he knows he can come to me if something online worries or confuses him."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s see how @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name talks to her mother about something she saw online."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.friend_male_1.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hey, look at this! People are saying it’s @data.characters.friend_male_1.name from our school."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No ways… look at what he is doing."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yeah… something doesn’t look right."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "People can fake videos now… make it look like someone did something they didn’t do. They can even put someone’s face on a naked body."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.friend_male_1.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Everyone is sharing it though… I know @data.characters.friend_male_1.name has not seen this. Should I send it to him?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yeah. I mean, everyone has seen it already anyway."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What if it’s not even real? That could mess things up for him. Maybe we shouldn’t share it…"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Later that afternoon, @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name comes home from school and finds her mother."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Mother, can I ask you something?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Of course."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you know if something online is real or not?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s a really good question. Many things online are not real - videos, pictures, written things, anything. Before you believe something or share it, it helps to ask: ‘Who shared this? Do I know them? Why would they want to share it?’"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And also just think: Could this cause problems for the person in the video or for others?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay, that makes sense. Thank you, mother."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let's think about what happened."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What does Mother do to help @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name think about this?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, staying calm helps your teen feel safe to talk."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask simple questions"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Exactly. Questions help your teen think about what they are seeing."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Talk about not sharing too quickly"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, pausing before sharing can prevent harm."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remind her she can always talk"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s right. By being open, we help our teens know they can trust and share with us."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name? should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What makes this situation difficult for @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The video may not be real"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Correct. It can be hard to know what is real online."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "She is pressured to share it"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s right. Teens may feel pressure when others are sharing something."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It could hurt someone"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Exactly. Sharing something like this can harm another person."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It can feel confusing"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, teens may feel unsure about what they are seeing."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember, if you aren’t sure just ask."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Think about:\n"
"\n"
"🙍🏾 **Who made it?** Knowing who created it can help you understand if it is trustworthy.\n"
"❓ **Why was it shared?** Some content is made to get attention or to hurt someone — not to show the truth.\n"
"⚠️ **Does it seem strange or too good to be true?** If something feels strange, it's worth pausing and thinking before trusting or sharing it.\n"
"💙 **Is it okay to share?** Check with the owner of the image or the person in the picture before sharing it, to prevent spreading something untrue or harmful."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_14.name.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What we see online is sometimes not real and can influence how we think and act. This can also be true for sexual content. Let’s see how @data.characters.f1_father.name starts a conversation with his son, @data.characters.f1_son_14.name."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_14.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_14.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name and @data.characters.f1_son_14.name are making a fire for a braai. @data.characters.f1_son_14.name looks at his phone to put on some music."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_14.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_son_14.name, you know how sometimes things just pop up on your phone?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yeah?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sometimes you’re just scrolling or searching for something totally normal, and suddenly there’s a video or picture of people without clothes. You weren’t even looking for that! Has that ever happened to you?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sometimes."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That makes sense. A lot of young people see things like that online. It can feel strange... or interesting... or confusing. Just know, you did nothing wrong by seeing it."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Porn is made to get attention, not to show real bodies or healthy relationships. In real relationships, people treat each other with respect and never pressure someone into doing something they do not want."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "If you ever see something that makes you uncomforable, or you’re just not sure about it, you can come to me. I promise to listen and not get angry, and we can talk about it. And if talking to me feels weird, you can talk to another adult you trust."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay, father, I will do that."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_14.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_son_14.name may feel confused or unsure"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, teens can feel curious, uncomfortable or confused after seeing sexual content. Talking can help."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_14.name? should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Why is it important for father to have this conversation with @data.characters.f1_son_14.name?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Correct. What is shown is often not real and can give confusing ideas about relationships."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_14.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_son_14.name needs to know he can talk"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s right. When teens feel safe to talk, they are more likely to ask for help."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_14.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ignoring it may create problems for @data.characters.f1_son_14.name"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, most teens see this content at some point. If we don’t talk, teens may try to figure things out on their own without guidance."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_14.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_14.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What simple rules could Father and @data.characters.f1_son_14.name make together to help @data.characters.f1_son_14.name avoid seeing sexual content?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Keep phones in shared spaces"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Charge phones outside the bedroom"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Talk about what to do if something pops up"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Check in regularly without blaming"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes. Simple, agreed rules can help teens see less of this and feel safer to ask for help."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Your first response can make a big difference. These four simple steps can help your teen feel safe to keep talking with you."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Stay calm and take a breath"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "If your teen tells you they have seen something upsetting or sexual online, try to stay calm before you respond. Your first reaction helps your teen decide whether it feels safe to keep talking with you."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ask and listen"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Try asking simple, open questions such as:\n"
"\n"
"“Can you tell me what happened?”\n"
"“How did it make you feel?”\n"
"“What do you think about what you saw?”\n"
"Listen without judging or rushing to solve the problem."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Reassure and support your teen"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"You could say:\n"
"“Thank you for telling me.”\n"
"“You did not do anything wrong.”\n"
"“We can work through this together.”\n"
"This helps reduce shame and makes it more likely your teen will come to you again."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "End with connection"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let your teen know they can always come to you if something online worries or confuses them."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some simple ways you can support your teen when they see or share things online that are confusing or sensitive."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "PREVENT WHAT YOU CAN"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"It’s impossible to protect teens from everything online, but simple routines can reduce exposure. \n"
"\n"
"Keep devices, including phones, in shared family spaces during the day and at night. Set a good example by following the same rules yourself."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Set up a central charging spot outside bedrooms. \n"
"\n"
"Connect with other parents to agree on similar rules - it’s easier for teens to accept rules that their friends’ families also follow."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "THINK BEFORE YOU SHARE"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Help your teen pause before sharing anything online. Remind them that some videos and pictures are not real or are made to get attention. Ask: Who made this? Why was it shared? Does it feel real? \n"
"\n"
"If a friend sends a sexual video, it is okay not to pass it on. Your teen can simply say, \"I don't send things like that.\""
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remind your teen that sharing sexual, upsetting or harmful content can hurt both others and themselves. Make sure they know not to share personal information online and to talk to a trusted adult if they are unsure."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "STAY CALM"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"If your teen sees something confusing or sexual online, stay calm and listen. \n"
"\n"
"Thank them for telling you. \n"
"\n"
"Reassure your teen that they did nothing wrong. Avoid blame or anger so they feel safe coming to you again."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Keep conversations open, without judging. If upsetting content keeps appearing, discuss simple steps you can take together to help reduce it."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "TALK RESPECT"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Teens often learn what relationships look like from what they see online. \n"
"\n"
"You can help correct that picture. Help your teen understand that real relationships should feel safe, respectful and comfortable for everyone."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Nobody should ever feel pressured to do something they do not want to do."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s practise how you might respond when your teen sees something online."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Scenario 1: Your teen shows you a video and says: “Everyone is sharing this. Do you think it is real?” How could you respond?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Stay calm and ask questions"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tell them not to watch things like that"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Say you are not sure and think together"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes. Staying calm and discussing together helps your teen think and make safer choices."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Not quite. Angry reactions or avoiding the conversation can stop your teen from sharing. Staying calm helps them feel safe to talk."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Scenario 2: Your teen accidentally saw porn on their phone. What could you say?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Get angry and blame them"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Reassure it’s not their fault"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Ignore it"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That may not work. Strong reactions or ignoring it can make your teen feel ashamed and stop them from sharing."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Stay calm and listen"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes. Staying calm and reassuring your teen helps them feel safe to talk and reduces shame."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This week’s home activity is to talk with your teen about something they have seen online. \n"
"\n"
"Ask your teen to tell you about something interesting they saw online or something that felt confusing or strange."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Remember to ask:** \n"
"\n"
"What do you think about it? Do you think it is real? Why do you think it was shared? How can this affect others? \n"
"\n"
"Listen without judging and thank your teen for sharing."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you talk with your teen about something they have seen online this week?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s great! By staying calm and talking together, you help your teen feel safe to share and make better choices online."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You can do it! Try asking your teen about something they have seen online. A simple “What have you been watching lately?” is a great way to start."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s okay. This kind of conversation can feel hard at first. Remember, staying calm and showing interest helps your teen feel safe to talk."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Well done for taking time for yourself today. 🎉 \n"
"\n"
"If you need more support, you can find additional resources and support services in the Parent Library under \"Online Safety\"."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here is a short video to help you slow down before you go"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When everything feels like it is falling apart And you can't help but raise your voice When all the frustrations are beginning to start Remember that you have a choice\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"You can take pause, you can count to 10 Play a game or do something fun You can phone a friend, someone to confide in Remember you're not the only one\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more Because I really couldn't love you more"
msgstr ""
